  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t巴克禮牧師，不念麻豆屠殺之惡，於賊酋夜遁之際，受市民性命之托，面見乃木希典將軍，告以臺南悛改之誠。皇軍乃列隊鼓樂而入，老幼皆簞食壺漿以迎。越明年，法律明而三權分，西學興而產業隆。自鄭氏入寇以來，二百年有如是乎？奇功既成，聖君賜以勳章之榮，萬民贈以捲軸之美。偉哉，巴克禮牧師！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWM1MzRmZjEzMWY4M2NiMGNiZTE5LmpwZz93aWR0aD05MzYmaGVpZ2h0PTk0OA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ec534ff131f83cb0cbe19.jpg?width=936&amp;height=948\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ec534ff131f83cb0cbe19.jpg?width=936&amp;height=948\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ec534ff131f83cb0cbe19.jpg?width=936&amp;height=948\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
